  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Global Flagship Events & B2C Partnerships Lead",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Description</strong></p><p>Zuler is a global leader in remote desktop and cloud computing, revolutionizing connectivity with cutting-edge cloud rendering and real-time communication technologies. With over 180 million installed devices and a team of experts from top tech companies, Zuler delivers high-performance solutions that empower users worldwide.</p><h3>Role Summary</h3><p>This role owns DeskIn’s <strong>global flagship event activations </strong>and <strong>B2C brand partnerships</strong>. You will turn major events, creator gatherings, and lifestyle communities into high-impact growth engines through co-marketing, on-site activations, and consumer-facing collaborations.<br /></p><p>Function: Community, Ecosystem, Growth</p><p>Location: Singapore<br /></p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Lead partnerships for <strong>global flagship events</strong> (tech, gaming, creator, lifestyle)</li><li>Secure B2C partners: <strong>hardware brands, peripherals, gaming brands, lifestyle tech</strong></li><li>Design scalable event collaboration models:<br /> (sponsorships, co-activation, bundles, UGC challenges, trials)</li><li>Build global pipeline (US creators, JP brands, TW communities, SEA gaming cafés)</li><li>Own partner lifecycle: outreach → deal → activation → performance review</li><li>Work closely with Events, KOL, and Social teams to maximize reach & conversion</li></ul><h3>Role Requirements</h3><ul><li>4–10 years in <strong>B2C partnerships, events activation, or ecosystem growth</strong></li><li>Proven experience activating partnerships at <strong>flagship or regional events</strong></li><li>Strong negotiation and relationship management skills</li><li>Experience in tech, gaming, or creator industries is a plus</li><li>Comfortable working across global markets</li></ul>",
